\s1 Antayiteeri apawopaeni  
\p
\v 1 Ipokaki Tajorentsi nojeekira naaka, ikantakina:  
\v 2 “¿Iitaka kaari okoñaatanta inampiki Israel ikenkithawaeteetziri paerani ikanteetziri: ‘Arika ithotero ashitanari kachori chochoki, riitaki itomipaeni tsiyaekitee raekiki.’?  
\v 3 Naaka Tajorentsi, pikemena nopaeriiro nowaero, eero papiiteero eerokaete pikenkithawaeteero ikenkithawaetziri paerani Israel-paeni.  
\v 4 Naaka ashitari maawoeni atziri, nashitari ipaapateetari eejatzi itomipaenipaeni. Ikaate kaariperotatsini, otzimatye ikame.   
\c 19  
\c 20  
\c 21  
\c 22  
\c 23  
\c 24  
\c 25  
\c 26  
\c 27  
\c 28  
\s1 Kaariperori ñaantsi ikamanteetziriri pinkatharitatsiri nampitsiki Tiro  
\p
\v 1 Ipokaki Tajorentsi jempe nojeeki naaka, ikantakina:  
\v 2 “Shirampari, eeroka noñaanatzi, piyaate pikamanteri iroka ñaantsi pinkatharitatsiri nampitsiki Tiro:  
\b  
\p ‘Iroka ikantaki Tajorentsi:  
\b  
\q1 Owanaana piñaaperowaetaka pishireki,  
\q1 pipinkathatashitakari tajorentsiniro  
\q1 riitaki jeekaentsiri iwinkatharimentoki tajorentsiniro  
\q1 othonka otapotakimi inkaare.  
\q1 Tema eeroka tee pitajorentsitzi, atziri pini,  
\q1 eeroka kenkithashiretashitacha apaniroeni ijeekitantakimi riyomento tajorentsiniro.   
\q1
\v 3 ¿Poshiyakaatzi pawijakiri okaatzi riyotanitari Daniel?  
\q1 ¿Tzimatsima nomanimotzimiri kaari piyotzi?   
\q1
\v 4 Tema roori piyotani, okaatzi paawiiri eeroka  
\q1 pimatakiro otzimimotzimi osheki koetyiimotzimiri,  
\q1 piyeekitakiro powantariri ooro eejatzi koriki.   
\q1
\v 5 Osheki pashiminthatawo eeroka pipimantawaetzi  
\q1 poshekyaakiro pashaahawo,  
\q1 rootaki pashaahawo ñaaperotakayimiri pishireki.   
\q1
\v 6 Rootaki ikantantari Tajorentsi:  
\q1 Pantzirorika riitaki yotanitakayimiri tajorentsiniro,   
\q1
\v 7 nokantakahaeyaawo ipoke paashinijatzi atziri rowayiritemi,  
\q1 mataperori iyatsimate atziripaeni,  
\q1 riitaki ameroni rojataamento rowamayemi,  
\q1 eeroka rompoje, owanaana pikameethatzi, yotaniri,  
\q1 aritaki papaawaeteeya pookawenteeyaawo powaneenkawo.   
\q1
\v 8 Rookaetemi inthomoyaaki,  
\q1 eerowa pikamita niyankyaaki inkaare.   
\q1
\v 9 ¿Eekiroma pikenkithashiretatziiri tajorentsiniro,  
\q1 arika piñaawakiri ikaate maemanetemini?  
\q1 ¡Arika rotaeyemi ompojemini  
\q1 tekatsira piitya eeroka atzirimacheeni pini!   
\q1
\v 10 Rowamayemi paashinijatzi atziri,  
\q1 poshiyeeyaari rompojeetziri kaariperoshireri.  
\q1 Naaka Tajorentsi, kenkithawaetatsiri,  
\q1 aritaki nokamantakimi.’”  
\v 11 Ikantakina eejatzi Tajorentsi:   
\q1
\v 12 “Atziri pini eeroka, iroka omampahaantsi pomampaakotyaari pinkatharitatsiri nampitsiki Tiro, pikanteri:  
\q1 Iroka iñaane Tajorentsi, ikantzi:  
\q1 Owanaana pikameethawitaka eeroka, yotani pikanta, owaneenkaki pikanta.   
\q1
\v 13 Pinampiwitakawo pankirentsimashiki Edén-ki, rashitakaawitakimiri Tajorentsi,  
\q1 Osheki owaneenkataka okantakaawo kantawaeyitachari mapiki poreryaari.  
\q1 Pithatanitari ooro rowetsikaetakimiri owakira pañaanaki.\f + \fr 28.13 \ft Ikanteetziri jaka “mapiki poreryaari”, riitaki ikanteetziri eejatzi: rubí, crisólito, jade, topacio, cornalina, jaspe, zafiro, granate eejatzi esmeralda.\f*   
\q1
\v 14 eenitatsi aayitatsiri, paamaawentyaari, pijeekaki ochempiki itajorentsitakaakiri Tajorentsi.  
\q1 Panashiwaetzi jempe ipiyotapaa ompokiro.   
\q1
\v 15 Tekatsi pikinakaashitya, kameethari pikanta owakira rowetsikaetakimi  
\q1 Roojatzi pikaariperotantanakari.   
\q1
\v 16 Tzimanaki osheki pashaahawo, osheki pikoshekawaetanaka, owanaana pikaariperotanaki.  
\q1 Rootaki nookantakimiri, tee nokowe pijeekimotena.  
\q1 Nomishitowakimi pijeekawitaha ochempiki rashitari Tajorentsi.  
\q1 Riitaki omishitowakimiri aayitatsiri, pitsipawitari pinampitawo ompokiromashiki.   
\q1
\v 17 Piñaakiro powaneenkata, owanaana piñaaperotanaka pishireki.  
\q1 Osheki omajontyaanakimi pishipakiryaanakira.  
\q1 Nookakimi jaawi, osheki pikaanitaki piñaakirira raminaminthatakimi pinkatharipaeni nomishitowakimira.   
\q1
\v 18 Owanaana pikaariperotaki, maperori okoweenkatakaakimi pashaahawo,  
\q1 Iwinkani rowaeta pitajorentsipankote.  
\q1 Rootaki nowantakari paamari jempe pijeeke eeroka, riitaki thonkaemini itaayimi.  
\q1 Iñahaemi pisamampotee jaawi.   
\q1
\v 19 Maawoeni atziri ikaate ñahaemini, osheki ithaawakaemi.  
\q1 Koweenkaki pikanteeya. Ashi powaero eero pitzimae.”   